Cape Verde’s Rating Outlook Raised to Stable by S&P as Economy Expands

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-05-24T10:41:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/cape-verde-s-rating-outlook-raised-to-stable-by-s-p-as-economy-expands.html
Standard & Poor’s  raised its outlook
on  Cape Verde ’s credit rating to stable from negative because of
“moderately strong growth prospects.”  Cape Verde’s B+ long-term and B short-term sovereign credit
ratings were affirmed, S&P said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  